def calculate_time_until_next_review(cutoff_time):
    """
    Tnh ton thi gian cn li cho n ln n tp tip theo.
    :param cutoff_time: datetime, thi im n tp tip theo
    :return: dict, cha hours, minutes, seconds cn li
    """
    delta = cutoff_time - timezone.now()
    total_seconds = int(delta.total_seconds())
    hours, remainder = divmod(total_seconds, 3600)
    minutes, seconds = divmod(remainder, 60)
